==Useful Info==
'''Spriggan enchanters''' are aggravating casters who rely on their [[Hexes]] to disable you before getting into melee and [[stab]]bing you with their [[dagger]]s or [[quick blade]]s. They can be found accompanying [[the Enchantress]] and in certain spriggan-themed vaults.

